import math

def calculate_minimum_packs(k: int, n: int, s: int, p: int) -> int:
    sheets_per_person = math.ceil(n / s)
    total_sheets_required = k / sheets_per_person
    packs_needed = math.ceil(total_sheets_required / p)
    return packs_needed
